{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban schools from requiring students to do Extended Project Qualifications (EPQs)",
        "additional_details": "Some schools require students to undertake an Extended Project Qualification (EPQ) as part of their studies. Schools justify these by saying that these projects provide transferable skills and are excellent opportunities, but we do not believe this is the case, and think schools and colleges should not be able to require students to undertake an EPQ.",
        "background": "I request the Government ban any school or college from requiring students to undertake an Extended Project Qualification (EPQ).",
